    "20599448": {
      "title": "The International Physical Activity Questionnaire modified for the elderly: aspects of validity and feasibility",
      "abstract": "OBJECTIVE: To modify the self-administered, short version of the International Physical Activity Questionnaire (IPAQ) for adults to be used in the elderly (aged 65 years and above), and to validate ..."
